      "message": "I think we can get all these in a base case and a recursive one?\n\n// ax + b...\nstatic inline F32 poly(F32 x, F32a a, F32a b) {\n    return a*x+b;\n}\n\n// ... ax^2 + bx + c, ax^3 + bx^2 + cx + d, etc.\ntemplate \u003ctypename... Rest\u003e\nstatic inline F32 poly(F32 x, F32a a, F32a b, Rest... rest) {\n    return poly(x, poly(x,a,b), rest...);\n}",
