      "writtenOn": "2020-04-04T21:15:23Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "oops, how 2011 of me... we can now do this all in one go!\n\n    // ax + b, ax^2 + bx + c, ax^3 + bx^2 + cx + d, etc.\n    template \u003ctypename... Rest\u003e\n    static inline F32 poly(F32 x, F32a a, F32a b, Rest... rest) {\n        if constexpr (sizeof...(rest) \u003d\u003d 0) {\n            return x*a+b;\n        } else {\n            return poly(x, x*a+b, rest...);\n        }\n    }",
